In the evening joyously drinking beer. In the morning pale and still.
(Finnish: Illalla hilpeänä kaljaa, aamulla kalpeana hiljaa.)

[I'll hit you] with a čokanjčićem [little rakija bottle], [you'll hit me] with a čokanjčićem.
(Serbian: Čokanjčićem ću te, čokanjčićem ćeš me.)

This fool never should drink wine, a short and dumb life he will live if he drinks.
(Spanish: Ese bobo vino nunca beber debe, vida boba y breve vivirá si bebe.)

After three drinks and another three,
and another three after the three drinks,
drink and drink (cause) devastation,
hors d'oeuvres pranks,
[nonsense word] section and glutton
33 rum drinks
followed by extreme trout pieces
in an instant might be thundered by a thunder.
(Spanish: Tras tres tragos y otros tres,
y otros tres tras los tres tragos,
trago y trago son estragos,
travesuras de entremés,
trapola tramo y tragón,
treinta y tres tragos de ron
tras trozos de trucha extremo,
en un tris los truene el trueno.)

If you drink don't drive, if you drive don't drink.
(Japanese: Nomu nara noru na, noru nara nomu na.)

A shill was driving a "Ferrari", went mad and crashed into the lamp-post.
(Russian: Фраер рулил в "Феррари", офонарел - зарулил в фонарь.)
